		'<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span><br></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span>绪论</span></b><b><span>	</span></b><b><span>Introduction &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b><b><span>	</span></b><b><span><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span><font face=\"微软雅黑 Light\">欢迎参加上海波音</font>2018员工敬业度调查! &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span><font face=\"微软雅黑 Light\">工作在我们的生活中占据了很重要的一部分，</font>它对个人的职业生涯与发展有着深远的影响。</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font face=\"微软雅黑 Light\">身为上海波音的一员，</font>您一定非常清楚公司在哪些方面做得好，以及哪些方面还需要加强."员工敬业度调查"让您有机会将您的意见及想法传达给公司，让公司通过了解员工对工作内容的反馈和建议，作为公司整体未来组织工作及员工需求的改善参考。</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span><font face=\"微软雅黑 Light\">我们感谢每一位员工在工作以及建议反馈方面做出的贡献，</font>让我们携手共同努力，将上海波音打造成为更美好的工作场所。 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Welcome to Boeing Shanghai " 2018 Engagement Survey " ! &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Work is an important part of our life and it takes up a large part of our life time. </span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>As a member of Boeing Shanghai you must have clear ideas about the areas where your company is doing well and areas where improvements are required. Engagement survey provides you with the access of giving feedback to our company. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>By sharing your opinions, we can have a better understanding of what you are thinking about in your work, which can help us to improve in the future. &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>We appreciate what you contribute both in work and feedback, and let us work together to make Boeing Shanghai a happier &amp; better place to work. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span><font face=\"微软雅黑 Light\">本次调查</font>,将请您针对以下方面提供您的看法 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>We would like to know your views on the following aspects: &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>1公司文化 Boeing Shanghai company culture &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>2公司战略 Company strategy &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>3运营效率 Operation Efficiency / Lean &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>4绩效管理 Performance Management &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>5安全和质量 Safety &amp; Quality &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>6黄金守则 Golden Rules</span><span>	</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>7员工沟通 Employee Communication &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>8团队合作 Team Work &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>9领导及管理效能 Leadership &amp; Management Effectiveness &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>10工作环境 Working Environment &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span><font face=\"微软雅黑 Light\">请您就以上方面的管理内容提供宝贵意见与看法</font>.答案并无对错之分,无论是正面或负面的的意见,您个人的真实回馈才能客观反映公司状况,让这份报告更有价值和说服力 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>You are strongly urged to share your views on both the strengths and weaknesses of the company. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Your honest opinions are important, whether positive or negative, and there are no right or wrong answers. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span>说明</span></b><b><span>	</span></b><b><span>Direction &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b><b><span>	</span></b><b><span><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span><font face=\"微软雅黑 Light\">本问卷共计</font>56个问题.请回答所有的问题.您大约只需要30分钟的时间来完成问卷填写</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>There are totally 56 questions, please answer every question in the survey. It should take you about 30 minutes to complete the survey &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span><font face=\"微软雅黑 Light\">请不要与他人讨论问卷内容</font>,您应就个人感觉来回答问题,而不是依您觉得其他人会怎么想来回答 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Please do not discuss with anyone else. Your answers should be based on your personal feelings, instead of what</span><span>	</span><span>&nbsp;you think others feel. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span><font face=\"微软雅黑 Light\">由于各问题问法会有所不同</font>,当您回答问题时,请先明确该问题的问法及回答方式,再进行作答 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>When answering the questions, please make sure that you are clear about the ways the questions are asked, as well as the ways the answers are required, as it may vary. </span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span>保密性</span></b><b><span>	</span></b><b><span>Confidentiality &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b><b><span>	</span></b><b><span><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span><font face=\"微软雅黑 Light\">您的回答将被视为最高机密</font>.在此我们向您保证本问卷仅被用做数据分析及公司制定改善计划.在做结果汇报时，会对个性化的信息进行相应处理，以确保填表人的机密性。</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>We will treat your responses as the strictest confidence.We guarantee that the questionnaires will only be used for analysis. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span>定义</span></b><b><span>	</span></b><b><span>Definition &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b><b><span>	</span></b><b><span><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span><font face=\"微软雅黑 Light\">在开始填写问卷之前，这里有一些对您填写问卷将有所帮助的定义。请仔细阅读并作适时地参考。</font> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Before we begin with the survey ,there are a couple of definitions which will be helpful in answering the questions. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>Please read these carefully and refer to them as necessary. &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>“公司”指的是上海波音 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>"Company" refers to Boeing Shanghai &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>“工作团队”指的是您最常直接参与之工作团队 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>"Work group" refers to the immediate group you work with most often &nbsp;</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>“部门”指的是您工作团队所隶属之部门 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span>	</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span>"Department" refers to the larger group of which your work group is a part</span></p>',
